dc_description_s: REMOTE DOWNLOAD NOT AVAILABLE - please contact data@library.columbia.edu for access. Tibet Provincial Trunk Roads, 2000 is a polyline theme representing provincial trunk roads in Tibet for 2000.  This data layer is part of the Tibet 2000 Township Census data set produced by the All China Marketing Research Co. and distributed by the University of Michigan, China Data Center.
